content:
The price for the Isuzu mu-X standard accessories are as follows:
- Carpet Floor Mat: Kes. 22,389
- Rubber Floor Mat: Kes. 10,198
- Door Visor: Kes. 12,659

Additionally, an optional accessory is available:
- Muffler Cutter: Kes. 6,629

Please note that these prices are subject to change and may vary based on location and availability. For the most accurate and up-to-date pricing information, it is recommended to contact your local Isuzu service center or dealer.
